title: Tropisch Nederland, Deel 4 [Tropical Dutch East Indies] in color! (1939)

sources.title: Tropisch Nederland, Deel 4 [Tropical Dutch East Indies] in color! (1939)
sources.description: This is part-4 of a 8 part documentary about the Dutch East Indies (currently Indonesia) just before WW-II. This footage has been meticulously restored, enhanced and colorized with the lastest A.I. video software.
